commits adultery with bathsheba and compounds the betrayal with murder but through the authors empathy and skill david also emerges as a fully realized character a man of passion and intelligence who navigates the ambiguities of belief loyalty ambition temptation and circumstance with uneven success product information▼▲ format paperbacknumber of pages vendor ww nortonpublication date dimensions   x   x  inchesisbn isbn  other customers also purchased add to cart add to wishlist body soul and life everlasting biblical anthropology and the monismdualism debate john w cooper john w cooper wm b eerdmans publishing co    trade paperback  retail  save   add to cart add to wishlist between two horizons wm b eerdmans publishing co    trade paperback  retail  save   add to cart add to wishlist salvation belongs to our god celebrating the bibles central story christopher jh wright christopher jh wright ivp academic    trade paperback  retail  save    stars out of   reviews add to cart add to wishlist lectures to my students charles h spurgeon charles h spurgeon christian focus    hardcover  retail  save   related products add to cart add to wishlist the book of psalms a translation with commentary robert alter robert alter ww norton    hardcover  retail  save    stars out of   reviews publishers description▼▲ acclaimed for its masterful new translation and insightful commentary the david story is a fresh vivid rendition of one of the great works in western literature alters translation paints not only the heroic picture of david in his fight with goliath but also portrays david as an ambitious calculating man with a flawed vision product reviews▼▲ be the first to write a review write review ask a question▼▲ have a question about this product ask us here find related products▼▲ books ebooks  audio  academic  biblical studies  old testament studies  historical books authorartist review▼▲ im the authorartist and i want to review the david story backtimes ask a question what wou